('ROBLOX: Pony Edition','http://www.roblox.com/games/253293579/My-Little-Pony-FiM-TPP-RP-2D','MMO',NULL,'<p>The game is made and played from an entire community of 8,000 members. It&rsquo;s a Roleplaying 2D game that is still under the works. We have an entire staff base working on the game and working on the project itself. We want to post this because there are rarely any other MLP games on ROBLOX anymore, and we are trying to keep the idea of ponies on ROBLOX alive, we are the only major active Brony group besides Roleplay is Magic.</p>\n<p><br />The Pony Project&rsquo;s goal is to keep developing games for the Brony community, inside and outside of ROBLOX. We receive about 1,000 visits a day. I personally submit this because I just feel like we aren&rsquo;t really involved in the Brony community that much, and we would love to be involved. We welcome to you join the game and enjoy it.</p>\n<p>Our community page is found here:</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.roblox.com/games/253293579/My-Little-Pony-FiM-TPP-RP-2D\">http://www.roblox.com/My/Groups.aspx?gid=851605</a></p>\n<p><br />Our website is found here:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://theponyprojectwebs.hamzahost.com/\">http://theponyprojectwebs.hamzahost.com/</a></p>',NULL,'Active',36,'2016-02-02 20:42:45','2016-02-02 20:42:45'),
('Ambient.Prologue','http://albdifferent.com/ambient-project/','Action/Adventure','https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-71WR2NaHWHQ/V4gdwZSMfFI/AAAAAAABpRE/EzRNiqlqNtU5_nBLE3GNgD49O8JMIFV9QCLcB/s1600/Capture.PNG','<p>A Steam Greenlight game developed by Bronies for Bronies. Set in the distant past with Celestia and Luna as playable characters the game currently as features such as combat, magic, flight and more!</p>',NULL,'Beta - In Development',37,'2016-07-14 23:23:02','2016-07-14 23:23:02'),
('Pinkamena','https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.catfood.pinkamena','Android Strategy Game','https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ji57DVi0iSE/V4ge5uqxkaI/AAAAAAABpRM/D_KrMe31iVE2TfmgQTU7xGw06nnqAiTnQCLcB/s1600/unnamed.png','<p>\"Pinkamena\" is a single-player game based on the popular \"Mafia\" genre of games, such as Town of Salem or Werewolf.</p>\n<p>You are Captain Silvermane, sent to a quiet little pony town by the Princess of the Sun herself to investigate reports of dark magic and murder.</p>\n<p>On arrival you find only a handful of terrified ponies remain. Among the innocent townsponies is a murderous gang of Changelings who have assumed pony form and are now working together to drain the innocents of their love to feed their insatiable Queen. This process is fatal to the ponies, of course.</p>\n<p>Bad as that is, you immediately realise there is an even worse threat in the town, an unstoppable force who will murder Pony and Changeling alike.</p>\n<p>Pinkamena.</p>\n<p>Please note that this game is a parody of the My Little Pony franchise. No canon images are used and all character names and images are randomly generated.</p>',NULL,'Complete',38,'2016-07-14 23:24:54','2016-07-14 23:24:54'),
('The Chaos Inside','http://pixelatedtechnology.tumblr.com/','2D Action-Platformer','https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-d5TOcF-kVPM/V4ggyZ9EplI/AAAAAAABpRc/MuB5SErKY9wPcD4LeEsMlpJUxS6aZE_9gCLcB/s1600/unnamed%2B%25281%2529.png','<p>The Elements of Harmony, as well as the ponies connected to them, have been seeming a little...off lately. They haven\'t really been acting themselves for a while...</p>',NULL,'In Development',39,'2016-07-14 23:31:32','2016-07-14 23:31:32'),
('Sulfur Nimbus - Hel\'s Elixir','https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/oddwarg/sulphur-nimbus-hels-elixir/description','Platformer/Action','https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-UGa7i9NPl8U/V97p6Kma5MI/AAAAAAABr44/-vd43K4DRUkoMlkYWFccEtCiaNdOXdO7QCLcB/s1600/Title.png','<p>Sulphur Nimbus works as a scouting bird on a merchant ship. One day, the captain is pressed for time and decides to take a shortcut across dangerous waters. This route goes past the island known as Dronnings&oslash;y, a name surrounded by ominous rumors. However, they are on schedule and all seems well, so Sulphur decides to fly a little closer to check it out. Suddenly a storm appears, as if by magic, and prevents her from returning to the ship . . .</p>',NULL,'In Development',40,'2017-06-07 02:27:02','2017-06-06 22:27:41'),
('Daring Do Flash Game','http://alexmakovsky.deviantart.com/art/Daring-Do-the-Flash-Game-ver-0-81-alpha-308653960','Platforming/Action','https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-eh_8OIeq06E/WTctsAP9r8I/AAAAAAAB2Vo/t9bdarMCfpsuFUJGeLImLlbgz6ebAzQMgCLcB/s1600/daring_do_the_flash_game_ver_0_81_alpha_by_alexmakovsky-d53rix4.jpg','<p>A platforming/action game where you play as Daring Do during a grand adventure! Meet interesting ponies, explore ancient ruins, and fight dangerous enemies.</p>',NULL,'In Development',41,'2017-06-06 22:36:47','2017-06-06 22:36:47'),
('Day Dreaming Derpy','https://rpgmaker.net/games/9424/','RPG','https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-vFkJG4EvHoc/WH1v048ntQI/AAAAAAABxH0/pr9xFQnAvEslSGu3todU6iskG0xV2BDgwCLcB/s1600/title_shot_by_sonicboy112-davlci7.png','<p>Derpy\'s the kind of mom that has to work all kinds of jobs around town to make end\'s meet; she\'s usually the first one up and the last one to bed. Ask around town and they\'ll say she\'s a trooper- an easy breeze that\'ll brighten up your day.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>She\'s also the kind of mom that accidentally burns dinner during soup night. Ask around town again and they\'ll say she\'s a real twister- leaves nothing unscathed in her wake.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Ask again and it seems like there\'s something weird going on around town; something that\'s making everyone lose precious hours of sleep. And it looks like no one but Derpy can do anything about it.&nbsp;<br /><br />Looks like the midnight shift just opened up...&nbsp;</p>',NULL,'Complete',42,'2017-06-07 02:38:42','2018-08-07 08:08:33'),
('Fall of AnterFOLD Series','https://fallofanderfold.jimdo.com/','Horror/Co-op','https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-DMf5sRZgHY0/WRUheqw3ENI/AAAAAAAB1V8/_Dj2ePZc5KczKyVpTyVM09HLWX_KtdnbwCLcB/s1600/unnamed.png','<p><strong>There are many Anterfold games now. Check the website for all listings!</strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Description:</strong>&nbsp;Fall of Anterfold is a cooperative game for two players where you will face not only with monsters,survival are a main condition which you must to done and to reach the end.</p>\n<p>In a single moment everything that you had seen, known, and loved disappeared. Anterfold fell not by the explosive destruction of bombs, but rather because of a mystic project known only as the&nbsp;\"Ring of Yorus\". What is still unknown is whether this was caused by some sort of virus or a massive weapon, but all that remains of the project is death.</p>\n<p>Thus began the age of big guns and powerful spells. Magic and technology were merged together, but these strides would not be the one legacy which&nbsp;remained of the&nbsp;\"Ring of Yorus\". All around the world energy holes started to show up which led dark creatures</p>\n<p>from another place into this world. These creatures were driven by a single need, Blood Lust.</p>\n<p>The remaining survivors founded six colonies:&nbsp;Derostraid, Nertenfild, Flaundskiel, Mortenholl, Kronleit, and Arheis. An Earth pony, Orangeflide, and a pegasus, Hover Clound, from Flaundskiel were assigned the task of&nbsp;exploring sector 2-A which approaches the center of the&nbsp;Dead City, Aronfide, but what secrets await them there?</p>\n<p>Perhaps answers to the question: What was the&nbsp;\"Ring of Yorus\"&nbsp;project? Or maybe something far more terrible...</p>',NULL,'Complete / In Development',43,'2017-06-07 10:40:50','2018-08-07 08:18:29'),
('Sunrise of Axoria','https://sunriseofaxoria.jimdo.com/','MOBA','https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-IEdQY8Z6bLs/WSt4WVk-voI/AAAAAAAB11k/f7Spi01iLdkAIwEj_JawnvN2hnJpII16wCLcB/s1600/unnamed%2B%25285%2529.png','<p>Basically a new pony themed MOBA game! Not much details besides that so far. You can sign up for testing below:</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://sunriseofaxoria.proboards.com/board/4/registration-on-alpha-test\">http://sunriseofaxoria.proboards.com/board/4/registration-on-alpha-test</a></p>',NULL,'In Development',44,'2017-06-06 22:44:07','2017-06-06 22:44:07'),
('Sector EQ','https://plus.google.com/108587811515961406246/posts/7X4o7EXXwnx','Platformer/Action','https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-uFxiU-2dNBk/WTcwupAmBeI/AAAAAAAB2Vs/tbj217pBHqQAtddgyJI3-eHob7EATvhygCLcB/s1600/unnamed%2B%25283%2529.png','<div><font face=\"inherit\">Sector EQ&nbsp;is a pony action/combat platformer.&nbsp;Weapons range from stone spears to triple-shot rocket launchers and include everything in between. If that isn\'t enough, you can choose up to four abilities to also unleash flamethrowers, grenades, deathballs, and many others.&nbsp;Whether you search for gems in caves and castles, rack up points in challenge levels, fight fellow ponies in battles to the death, or strengthen/ruin friendships in multiplayer, there is sure to be action-packed, equine carnage.<br /></font></div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div><font face=\"inherit\"><strong>Trailer:</strong>&nbsp;<font color=\"#000000\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_SAfSdx_D7M\" target=\"_blank\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?hl=en&amp;q=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v%3D_SAfSdx_D7M&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1496948290878000&amp;usg=AFQjCNE0L-Srxub-Wu4BLM-6WXeKnMBXFw\">https://www.youtube.<wbr />com/watch?v=_SAfSdx_D7M</a></font></font></div>\n<div><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"inherit\"><strong>Website:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://meowinc.yolasite.com/\" target=\"_blank\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?hl=en&amp;q=https://meowinc.yolasite.com&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1496948290878000&amp;usg=AFQjCNGJqIIqBZF1-CQR7gGyzXAf0WNU6Q\">https://meowinc.<wbr />yolasite.com</a></font></div>\n<div><font face=\"inherit\"><strong>Twitter:</strong>&nbsp;<font color=\"#000000\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/MrMeows1\" target=\"_blank\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?hl=en&amp;q=https://twitter.com/MrMeows1&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1496948290878000&amp;usg=AFQjCNEOKjQKQ_f8_bETRmg8065dWj5OOA\">https://twitter.com/<wbr />MrMeows1</a></font></font></div>',NULL,'Complete',45,'2017-06-07 02:47:18','2017-06-07 19:10:00'),
('The Town That Feared Nightfall','http://www.rpgmakercentral.com/topic/39580-the-town-that-feared-nightfall-demo/','Horror/Mystery','https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-fge_NJX9hkE/WTcxxGWVuwI/AAAAAAAB2Vw/h2wT8vfwinoiQNI1fkpy6mJvW8-y4nU0ACLcB/s1600/2e1fvrr.jpg','<p>A small town is suddenly gripped with fear as a killer randomly picks them off at night, and only you can save them if you\'re quick enough to find them.</p>\n<p><strong><em>Average Demo Time:</em></strong>&nbsp;30 minutes at most</p>\n<p><strong><em>Game Progression:&nbsp;</em></strong>At the moment the game only goes up to the end of night 2, which can end in a couple of ways. There are unfinished bits, like characters having no lines at certain parts. I\'m trying to mainly focus on the story and important moments, but I will go back and add character lines after I get enough of the story done. The game will take a long time to finish and fully write, since there are more than 1 outcome to certain cutscenes, hence why you\'ll see characters just standing idly and mute.</p>',NULL,'In Development',46,'2017-06-06 22:50:55','2017-06-06 22:50:55'),
('Gardens of Equestria: The Coming Storm','http://gardensofequestria.com/','RPG/Action','https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-IpVA2742S58/WTc9LzD6AGI/AAAAAAAB2WI/gzWDdegYSeAbXi05xLah9DHFWl-JTmnSwCLcB/s1600/nowavailable2.png','<p>A DLC-sized story-driven expansion featuring over 67 levels, a new worldspace, new fully voiced companions and more, GoE will bring the Mojave and Equestria closer than ever before.</p>',NULL,'In Development',47,'2017-06-06 23:40:17','2017-06-06 23:40:17'),
