('Age of Empires 2 HD','http://1.bp.blogspot.com/--3vWjidjJwE/U2gDXhoNyVI/AAAAAAAA10E/XRg2B4iywEM/s1600/age_of_empires__the_age_of_ponies___clean_by_joseph_hicks-d4u9itp.png','<div>Modifications for Age of Empires 2 HD on Steam currently include a download to change the intro movie and a download that adds around 500 pony quotes to the game.</div>\n<div><br /><strong><a href=\"http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=142282971&amp;searchtext=pony\">Intro Mod</a></strong></div>\n<div><strong><a href=\"http://steamcommunity.com/workshop/filedetails/?id=166242124\">Taunt Mod</a></strong>&nbsp;</div>',NULL,2,'2014-07-15 09:50:06','2017-06-06 23:27:15'),
('Alpha Centauri','http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-YmWIDuL_eKY/U3vAGXnqKUI/AAAAAAAA284/4a430rHfp0Q/s1600/Capture.PNG','<p>Mods in Alpha Centauri are a lot like the Civilization mods: pony factions, leaders, ect<br /><br /><strong><a href=\"http://ryuuproductions.blogspot.de/2013/09/alpha-centauri-pony-mod-08.html\">Alpha Centauri Pony Mod</a></strong></p>',NULL,3,'2014-07-15 09:50:24','2017-06-06 23:27:19'),
('Amnesia: The Dark Descent','http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-w-hZ5Jefe60/U2gFNv2jTCI/AAAAAAAA10Q/3Tp7JlYr-uw/s1600/fluttershy_in_amnesia_by_angelofhapiness-d4slno9.jpg','<p>Current mods for Amnesia include a download that lets you play as the mane 6 in the game with pony sounds, height, and other modifications made for realism.<br /><br /><strong><a href=\"http://www.moddb.com/mods/mane-six-mod\">Mane 6 Mod</a></strong></p>',NULL,4,'2014-07-15 09:50:41','2017-06-06 23:27:23'),
('Angry Birds','http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-Z3aGuFKVZls/U2gHN9K5TfI/AAAAAAAA10c/NsVrO8h-y7g/s1600/Capture.PNG','<p>Modifications of Angry Birds at the moment consist of a Google Chrome and Firefox mod that changes characters in the base game to ponies!<br /><br /><strong><a href=\"http://angryponies.herokuapp.com/\">Angry Ponies Mod</a></strong></p>',NULL,5,'2014-07-15 09:52:04','2017-06-06 23:27:32'),
