('Beat Hazard','http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-3xyjbtWJNYE/U3u7K9W5mYI/AAAAAAAA28Y/vXE8Ce4JotE/s1600/beat+hazard.png','<p>Beat Hazard Ultra, Shadow Operations DLC required<br /><a href=\"http://www.coldbeamgames.com/\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.coldbeamgames.com/</a><br /><br />This photo seizure inducing space arcade shooter creates waves of enemies according to your music!<br />For many years Super Pony Beat was the only way to bring Pony into the game -although enough fun already, the recently released Shadow operations DLC offers the ability to bring even more Pony right to the action as you are able to create your very own strobing, lazer packed Pony Space Ships. The community came up with a huge variety of pony ships, ranging from Rainbow over Derpy and many others to the Great and Powerful strobing Trixie. A few of the many possible ships in the hangar are given here as an example:<br /><br />RD:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=250589975&amp;searchtext=\" target=\"_blank\">http://steamcommunity.com/<u></u>shar<wbr />edfiles/filedetails/?id=<u></u>250589<wbr />975&amp;searchtext=</a><br />Cloudsdale Juggernout:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=250945556&amp;searchtext=\" target=\"_blank\">http://steamcommunity.com/<u></u>shar<wbr />edfiles/filedetails/?id=<u></u>250945<wbr />556&amp;searchtext=</a><br />Derpy:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=250939329&amp;searchtext=\" target=\"_blank\">http://steamcommunity.com/<u></u>shar<wbr />edfiles/filedetails/?id=<u></u>250939<wbr />329&amp;searchtext=</a><br />Trixie:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=251235866&amp;searchtext=\" target=\"_blank\">http://steamcommunity.com/<u></u>shar<wbr />edfiles/filedetails/?id=<u></u>251235<wbr />866&amp;searchtext=</a><br />Pinkie:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=252432089&amp;searchtext=\" target=\"_blank\">http://steamcommunity.com/<u></u>shar<wbr />edfiles/filedetails/?id=<u></u>252432<wbr />089&amp;searchtext=</a><br />Twi:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=250744161&amp;searchtext=\" target=\"_blank\">http://steamcommunity.com/<u></u>shar<wbr />edfiles/filedetails/?id=<u></u>250744<wbr />161&amp;searchtext=</a><br /><br />Here is a short gameplay Video -seizure warning!!!:<br /><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Rp5C-5AgCbo\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?<u></u><wbr />v=Rp5C-5AgCbo</a><br /><br />Join the fun, play your music, create and play your pony ship!</p>',NULL,7,'2014-07-15 09:52:39','2017-06-06 23:27:40'),
('Cave Story','http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-bM-Imgw5Arw/U164ygQtkHI/AAAAAAAA1Uw/NtexI-YzlcE/s1600/229262__UNOPT__safe_lyra_game_artist-dirkos_cave-story_5103ac3da4c72dd0200000ce.jpg.jpg','<div>Relive the wonder of Cave Story with ponies as you dive into these sprite and text replacements mods for the game. Play as either Lyra, Derpy, or Berry Punch.<br /><br />Another modification for Cave Story switches up a little more than the Lyra, Derpy, and Berry Punch mods. Includes sprite switches for many other characters other than the main hero.</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div><strong><a href=\"http://www.equestriadaily.com/2013/03/play-cave-story-with-ponies_16.html\">Article on Game Mod</a></strong></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://www.datafilehost.com/download-66966f19.html\"><strong>Cave Derpy</strong></a></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://www.datafilehost.com/download-9cd52682.html\"><strong>Cave Lyra</strong></a></div>\n<div>\n<div><strong><a href=\"http://www.datafilehost.com/download-21d29716.html\">Cave Berry</a></strong></div>\n<div><strong><a href=\"http://cave.gamebanana.com/sprites/3791\">My Little Cave Story</a></strong></div>\n</div>',NULL,8,'2014-07-15 09:53:00','2017-06-06 23:27:43'),
