('0 A.D.',NULL,'<p>Only current mod adds ponies to the 0 A.D. experience!</p>\n<p>-Ponies Ascendant:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://lordgood.deviantart.com/journal/Ponies-Ascendant-v-19-Unicorns-541820036\">Download</a></p>',NULL,36,'2016-02-03 06:12:29','2016-02-02 20:13:17'),
('Warcraft 2','https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-8IuR3rfySko/V4ghElHVd1I/AAAAAAABpRg/-aS3CYe1QXcBw3BH8Rly2EGnCaOpk8tbACLcB/s1600/cc7cc040-d5af-4e46-a480-0d4bc211aedd.png','<pre class=\"aLF-aPX-K0-aPE aLF-aPX-aLK-ayr-auR\">\"All-Team Organizer\" is a graphics/sound mod for Warcraft 2. <br />Somehow, the original game\'s units and balance fit really well <br />to be ponified. So, no gameplay changes were really required. <br />We have ponies building their bases that look like Ponyville, <br />fighting each other for dominance, landing on enemy bridgeheads <br />under fire from Pinkie Pie\'s party cannons hidden everywhere, <br />supported by CMC battle fleet. <br /><br />Some choices for original unit\'s ponification are really, like, lol. <br />For example, Paladin is Pinkie Pie, so her abilities are <br />Pinkie Sense (ex-Holy Vision), Healing, Exorcism (to expel Trixie).\n\nHave fun!\n\n---\n\nThe Story (or how it all came to this).\n\nRemember how you earned the title of Ponyville\'s All-Team Organizer? <br />An achievement to be proud! You\'ve learned that sometimes you got to <br />rely on your friends\'... conventional abilities. <br />And Princess Celestia relies on your teams and, <br />and your loyalty is being generously rewarded.\n\nHowever, there are secrets in Equestria even you are not supposed to<br />know. Thr magical artifacts that can shift the balance and <br />shake the very foundations of Equestria, the mysterious Mirror Pool <br />and the Crystal Mirror, hidden far from curious eyes. <br />Not far enough, however.\n\nDiscord finds out about the mirror pool and turns it into a powerful <br />weapon that allows him to multiply ponies he assembled through <br />intrigues and fear. His aim is to spread havoc unseen before all <br />across Equestria.\n\nOur only chance now is to unleash the power of the Crystal Mirror <br />hidden deep beneath the Canterlot Castle.\nAs you gather your remaining loyal friends and prepare to make <br />the leap through the mirror, Princess Celestia informs you that this<br />war will not be fought on Equestrian territory, but in another <br />dimension, so to save the world of ponies from the havoc of... <br />well, S3E3.\n\n----\n\nInstallation.\n\nOk, I lied: the mod is fow Wargus 2.3. Don\'t ask. <br />You got to have a Warcraft 2 CD or Image to run this, <br />and this is the hardest part. <br />I recommend Warcraft 2: Battle.Net Edition CD oe image. <br />It\'s illegal to download it via torrents.\n\nOnce you have the image, mount it.\n\nThen download and install Stratagus 2.3\n\nThen download and install Wargus 2.3 <br />(specify the WC2:BNE image folder)\n\nThen you unpack contents of the mod archive into your Wargus folder.\n\nStart a Tides of Darkness Campaign.\n\n---\n\nKnown bugs: Wargus is little buggy. <br />Right now multiplayer doesn\'t work, so we\'re waiting for this issue <br />to get fixed. You can get such bugs as Transports getting stuck. <br />If the game doesn\'t start, try to run is as administrator.<br /><br /><a href=\"http://www.moddb.com/mods/all-team-organizer\">http://www.moddb.com/mods/all-team-organizer</a></pre>',NULL,37,'2016-07-15 19:33:43','2016-07-14 23:46:52'),
