('Fallout 4',NULL,'<div>FancyPants has released a Fallout 4 Race Mod that includes Ponies!</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div><a href=\"https://mods.bethesda.net/#en/workshop/fallout4/mod-detail/2872154\" target=\"_blank\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?hl=en&amp;q=https://mods.bethesda.net/%23en/workshop/fallout4/mod-detail/2872154&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1496874239525000&amp;usg=AFQjCNE5QKK3so_uG543u8trjieS4_M6lQ\">https://mods.bethesda.net/#en/<wbr />workshop/fallout4/mod-detail/<wbr />2872154</a></div>\n<div><a href=\"https://mods.bethesda.net/#en/workshop/fallout4/mod-detail/2872197\" target=\"_blank\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?hl=en&amp;q=https://mods.bethesda.net/%23en/workshop/fallout4/mod-detail/2872197&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1496874239525000&amp;usg=AFQjCNFBlLezVBqlUesKrH4tLa0JDTY-Ig\">https://mods.bethesda.net/#en/<wbr />workshop/fallout4/mod-detail/<wbr />2872197</a><br />\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>Not only that, The MLP HUD mod has seen some big changes! It now includes Character STATS, Modifications to the&nbsp;Perk Chart, and several other new features.</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div><a href=\"http://www.nexusmods.com/fallout4/mods/660/\" target=\"_blank\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?hl=en&amp;q=http://www.nexusmods.com/fallout4/mods/660/?&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1496874239525000&amp;usg=AFQjCNGVETnY3Rh1TZ4pjz1rFwpnjv5RlA\">http://www.nexusmods.com/fallo<wbr />ut4/mods/660/?</a></div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>Crimes Against Nature and Pony Race are now available on Nexus too!&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.nexusmods.com/fallout4/mods/19040/\" target=\"_blank\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?hl=en&amp;q=http://www.nexusmods.com/fallout4/mods/19040/&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1496874239529000&amp;usg=AFQjCNG-MB5CGBHFXGH-n4WWFjgXsnyWkg\">http://www.nexusmods.com/<wbr />fallout4/mods/19040/</a></div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div><br />\n<div><strong>Pixel\'s MLP Texture Pack by Pixeltripper</strong></div>\n<br />\n<div>MLP texture pack to liven up the Wasteland a little bit for all the pony Vault Dwellers out there.</div>\n<br />\n<div><a href=\"http://www.nexusmods.com/fallout4/mods/2882/\" target=\"_blank\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?hl=en&amp;q=http://www.nexusmods.com/fallout4/mods/2882/&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1496874239558000&amp;usg=AFQjCNFPjJd3MJJK-pP9eTPN1WrctGzX2Q\">http://www.nexusmods.com/<wbr />fallout4/mods/2882/</a></div>\n<br />\n<div><strong>Fallout Ponified by Valykry</strong></div>\n<br />\n<div>Replacing many billboards, posters, books, paintings &amp; items (approximately 600 re-textures altogether).</div>\n<br />\n<div><a href=\"http://www.nexusmods.com/fallout4/mods/5032/\" target=\"_blank\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?hl=en&amp;q=http://www.nexusmods.com/fallout4/mods/5032/&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1496874239558000&amp;usg=AFQjCNGwJx-wROJ1vncR73qOQmEFQExvew\">http://www.nexusmods.com/<wbr />fallout4/mods/5032/</a></div>\n<br />\n<div><strong>Mare in the Moon by North</strong></div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>Cartoon horses in the blasted hellscape.</div>\n<br />\n<div><a href=\"http://www.nexusmods.com/fallout4/mods/375/\" target=\"_blank\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?hl=en&amp;q=http://www.nexusmods.com/fallout4/mods/375/&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1496874239558000&amp;usg=AFQjCNGBP7mYIsAOM3Gj-sr6TYTIRZWbjA\">http://www.nexusmods.com/<wbr />fallout4/mods/375/</a></div>\n<br />\n<div><strong>MLP Remembrance by Captainx16</strong></div>\n<br />\n<div>Changes the main menu video and song to a gorgeous castle room with stained glass featuring the Mane 6.</div>\n<br />\n<div><a href=\"http://www.nexusmods.com/fallout4/mods/11185/\" target=\"_blank\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?hl=en&amp;q=http://www.nexusmods.com/fallout4/mods/11185/&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1496874239558000&amp;usg=AFQjCNFBgi_hUOCS6SIWM2u-pgG9h9tv2w\">http://www.nexusmods.com/<wbr />fallout4/mods/11185/</a></div>\n<br />\n<div><strong>Equestria Friendship Radio by FlamerunnerFirestom</strong></div>\n<br />\n<div>This mod adds a new radio station that uses 20 songs that are MLP related or made by Brony musicians.</div>\n<br />\n<div><a href=\"http://www.nexusmods.com/fallout4/mods/10190/\" target=\"_blank\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?hl=en&amp;q=http://www.nexusmods.com/fallout4/mods/10190/&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1496874239558000&amp;usg=AFQjCNHRoi_ogMsuEeqsGAWyiEKGE-VLYw\">http://www.nexusmods.com/<wbr />fallout4/mods/10190/</a></div>\n<br />\n<div><strong>Little Mac\' by wolftak</strong></div>\n<br />\n<div>The Little Mac from Fallout: Equestria.</div>\n<br />\n<div><a href=\"http://www.nexusmods.com/fallout4/mods/9867/\" target=\"_blank\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?hl=en&amp;q=http://www.nexusmods.com/fallout4/mods/9867/&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1496874239558000&amp;usg=AFQjCNGU9k5GHrHD7HJ-xiYRTJOw1F5ttQ\">http://www.nexusmods.com/<wbr />fallout4/mods/9867/</a></div>\n<br />\n<div><strong>Littlepip Pipboy Background by Neuro</strong></div>\n<br />\n<div>This small mod adds Littlepip to the background of your PipBoy. She will be visible on all the screens, including the map screen.</div>\n<br />\n<div><a href=\"http://www.nexusmods.com/fallout4/mods/1935/\" target=\"_blank\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?hl=en&amp;q=http://www.nexusmods.com/fallout4/mods/1935/&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1496874239558000&amp;usg=AFQjCNELsuxkn8FKfQCMiraa7YhgHRXyyQ\">http://www.nexusmods.com/<wbr />fallout4/mods/1935/</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>',NULL,41,'2017-06-07 11:13:09','2017-06-07 01:36:06'),
('Fallout 3',NULL,'<div><strong>My Little Pony Fallout is Magic by clanky4</strong></div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>My Little Pony: Fallout is Magic adds ponies to Fallout 3. Several different pony followers can be found near Canterbury Commons.</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div><a href=\"http://www.nexusmods.com/fallout3/mods/21506/\" target=\"_blank\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?hl=en&amp;q=http://www.nexusmods.com/fallout3/mods/21506/&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1496874239558000&amp;usg=AFQjCNEwJwv1H_oI76Gcy-l9V0qnFKpxoA\">http://www.nexusmods.com/<wbr />fallout3/mods/21506/</a></div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div><strong>My Little Pony Texture Pack Plus by JHawk1666</strong></div>\n<div><br class=\"m_-8750118267163653388kix-line-break\" />This mod replaces some of the chems and Nuka-Cola products with their Fallout Equestria counterparts as well as much of the related in-game text.</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div><a href=\"http://www.nexusmods.com/fallout3/mods/19791/\" target=\"_blank\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?hl=en&amp;q=http://www.nexusmods.com/fallout3/mods/19791/&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1496874239558000&amp;usg=AFQjCNHXaf2NrIGu7Li4HMbpTS2ILvKfiQ\">http://www.nexusmods.com/<wbr />fallout3/mods/19791/</a></div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div><strong>Pony Slides and Load Screens by Mattatatta</strong></div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>This mod replaces all of the slides from the GOAT exam with versions using the ponies from My Little Pony: Friendship is Magic.</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div><a href=\"http://www.nexusmods.com/fallout3/mods/16449/\" target=\"_blank\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?hl=en&amp;q=http://www.nexusmods.com/fallout3/mods/16449/&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1496874239558000&amp;usg=AFQjCNFSYshrEX_p26HHiMq-qpotdFqp3Q\">http://www.nexusmods.com/<wbr />fallout3/mods/16449/</a></div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div><strong>Pony PipBoy Photo by Mattatatta</strong></div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>Choose from four different ponies to have smiling at you from your PipBuck: Rainbow Dash, Fluttershy, Littlepip or Steelhooves!</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div><a href=\"http://www.nexusmods.com/fallout3/mods/16096/\" target=\"_blank\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?hl=en&amp;q=http://www.nexusmods.com/fallout3/mods/16096/&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1496874239558000&amp;usg=AFQjCNEVtDSiEiG-V-hbiBOgw-BRMgGo4w\">http://www.nexusmods.com/<wbr />fallout3/mods/16096/</a></div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div><strong>My Little Pony - PipBoy Background Replacers by Werne</strong></div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>There are ten background replacers: Applejack, Rarity, Fluttershy, Pinkie Pie, Twilight Sparkle, Rainbow Dash, Luna, Celestia, Derpy Hooves and Zecora.<br class=\"m_-8750118267163653388kix-line-break\" />Added Luna by request from TheTemeraire.</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div><a href=\"http://www.nexusmods.com/fallout3/mods/16977/\" target=\"_blank\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?hl=en&amp;q=http://www.nexusmods.com/fallout3/mods/16977/&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1496874239558000&amp;usg=AFQjCNEeedIZrVqSu0J5NZK5oPIw3Jc9XA\">http://www.nexusmods.com/<wbr />fallout3/mods/16977/</a></div>',NULL,42,'2017-06-07 03:19:16','2017-06-07 01:36:04'),
