('World of Warcraft',NULL,'<div><strong>My Little Pony WeakAuras Texture Mod Pack</strong></div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>This is a modification of the Types.lua file found in WeakAuras/WeakAuras 2 to display custom My Little Pony textures.</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div><a href=\"http://www.wowinterface.com/downloads/info22282-MyLittlePonyWeakAurasTextureModPack.html\" target=\"_blank\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?hl=en&amp;q=http://www.wowinterface.com/downloads/info22282-MyLittlePonyWeakAurasTextureModPack.html&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1496874239559000&amp;usg=AFQjCNHGRotCpV0c9iIxzmwgU-uZGCylhA\">http://www.wowinterface.com/<wbr />downloads/info22282-<wbr />MyLittlePonyWeakAurasTextureMo<wbr />dPack.html</a></div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div><strong>My Little Companion</strong></div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>My Little Companion is an addon that places a small pony on your screen. You can set the area that the pony can walk around in by changing the size and location of the green box.</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div><a href=\"http://mods.curse.com/addons/wow/my-little-companion\" target=\"_blank\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?hl=en&amp;q=http://mods.curse.com/addons/wow/my-little-companion&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1496874239559000&amp;usg=AFQjCNGHDD80-VybaKzQbQy97rIudgUfbg\">http://mods.curse.com/addons/<wbr />wow/my-little-companion</a></div>',NULL,44,'2017-06-07 03:27:10','2017-06-07 01:36:00'),
