('Mine Little Crafty',NULL,'Server','Minecraft',NULL,'<p>Hey there, I\'m the owner of Mine Little Crafty and I\'m here to submit some info about our Minecraft server! I actually just threw together a brand new trailer earlier today as well:<br /><br /><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uDtU4aUglsY\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?<wbr />v=uDtU4aUglsY</a><br /><br />What we have to offer:<br />- Canon Equestria map full of city replications that are both staff and player built as well as a Fanon continent for player-created cities to go onto!<br />- Large Freebuild world that is meant for casual construction and survival gameplay<br />- An Amplified Factions world open to anyone to create and run their own Faction! PvP based, and hard difficulty survival for players who enjoy a challenge!<br />- Survival Games on an MLP:FiM themed arena! Fully automated and available around the clock, players can join and fight whenever they\'d like!<br /><br />We\'re open to people of all kinds and hope to continue to establish a friendly community that can welcome in interests from all over! Feel free to ask any questions if and when they arise!<br /><br />Mine Little Crafty IP:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://mc.squarehorse.com/\" target=\"_blank\">mc.SquareHorse.com</a><br />Our website: SquareHorse.com</p>',7,'2014-09-12 01:59:18','2014-09-12 01:59:18'),
('Ponyville Square Server',NULL,'Server','Minecraft','http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-JGksTwvwFBs/U2u1wFEQPwI/AAAAAAAA1_I/HdVGJj9pNMc/s1600/unnamed+(15).jpg','<p>Ponyville Square is a Minecraft server where fans of My Little Pony and other fandoms can come and explore worlds built to the highest quality. From our famous full-scale replica of Equestria, to the survival/RP Equestria: Colonizations adventure, and further still to the world of Undertale and more, there\'s something here for everyone to enjoy.&nbsp;</p>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>Builders can come and test their merit and help build our showcase worlds and be the envy of others. Role-Players can get together with friends and explore fully detailed and painstakingly designed maps. To those who want to team up and work togeher to survive, we got you covered with our server-side modded survival world Equestria: Colonizations. And finally, to everyone else, we also have a flatland free-build world were everyone can build and have fun!</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n<div>Main Server ip:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://mc.ponyvillesquare.com/\" target=\"_blank\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?hl=en&amp;q=http://mc.ponyvillesquare.com&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1480884889215000&amp;usg=AFQjCNExYUUQUQE89lpOAcOfG8JtOpKu1w\">mc.ponyvillesquare.com</a></div>\n<div>Colonizations ip:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://survival.ponyvillesquare.com/\" target=\"_blank\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?hl=en&amp;q=http://survival.ponyvillesquare.com&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1480884889215000&amp;usg=AFQjCNE7UajFKqzjWGajauQtCROQLthM2A\">survival.ponyvillesquare.com</a></div>\n<div>Webpage:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.ponyvillesquare.com/forums/\" target=\"_blank\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?hl=en&amp;q=https://www.ponyvillesquare.com/forums/&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1480884889215000&amp;usg=AFQjCNGSXC4-QsofxwyJXRD-sgQR_7gMSg\">https://www.<wbr />ponyvillesquare.com/forums/</a></div>\n</div>',8,'