('Pony Concordia Minecraft Server',NULL,'Server','Minecraft','http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-1mrV0roz_UI/VrEPyMylR7I/AAAAAAABieI/0fDyDu0CWsA/s1600/1d0fb9ab-bc7d-4a2b-ba6b-d2d5bda625e1.png','<p>Pony Concordia is a My Little Pony: Friendship is Magic themed Minecraft role-playing server.</p>\n<p>This community is run by a group of dedicated My Little Pony fans and are continuously working round the clock to not only let you see Equestria, but to actually become a pony from My Little Pony.</p>\n<p>We have an incredibly detailed world based on Equestria featured in the show; where all the adventure, mystery, and fun that you would expect to find in Equestria awaits. &nbsp;All of the annual events as depicted in the series such as Nightmare Night, Grand Galloping Gala, and Hearth&rsquo;s Warming, are held on the server usually as a big role-play event with special perks and prizes across the entire event.</p>\n<p>We also offer a creative free build world and a vanilla survival world should you wish to take a break from the excitement in Equestria.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Website:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.ponyconcordia.com/\">http://www.ponyconcordia.com/</a></p>\n<p>Server IP:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://mc.ponyconcordia.com/\">mc.ponyconcordia.com</a></p>',24,'2016-02-03 01:20:51','2016-02-02 20:21:47'),
('The Bronies United Gaming Clan - All Games',NULL,'Clan','All Games',NULL,'<p>The Bronies United Gaming Clan - All Games</p>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div><a href=\"http://bugc.tk/\" target=\"_blank\">http://bugc.tk</a></div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>The Bronies United Gaming Clan is a clan for all types of multiplayer games there is! While we are a clan for any game, we do still have more commonly played games compared to others. We\'re most invested in games like Town of Salem, Minecraft, Terraria and SMITE.</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>To join, you must contact Dash at&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:writersfrombeyond@outlook.com\" target=\"_blank\">writersfrombeyond@outlook.com</a>&nbsp;and remember, love and tolerance is best!</div>',25,'2016-02-02 20:37:12','2016-02-02 20:37:12'),
