('CinemaQuestria\'s Friday Game Night',NULL,'All Purpose Gaming Host','Voted On','https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-5AE7akDSKJE/WEMyPvviDpI/AAAAAAABvmI/LQeVhGtmt3ER4mxeG2E2-8xphMidXnKVgCLcB/s320/unnamed1.png','<div id=\"m_-7152026281445257199yiv8847588781yui_3_16_0_ym18_1_1458949357220_7194\">Hello bronies!</div>\n<div id=\"m_-7152026281445257199yiv8847588781yui_3_16_0_ym18_1_1458949357220_7193\" dir=\"ltr\">CinemaQuestria\'s weekly Friday Night Game is an event dedicated to multiplayer video games! If you are into good fun with other gamers, than this event is for you!</div>\n<div id=\"m_-7152026281445257199yiv8847588781yui_3_16_0_ym18_1_1458949357220_7278\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div id=\"m_-7152026281445257199yiv8847588781yui_3_16_0_ym18_1_1458949357220_7192\" dir=\"ltr\">During the week, you can suggest games we should add into the list for future game nights&nbsp;<span id=\"m_-7152026281445257199yiv8847588781yui_3_16_0_ym18_1_1458949357220_7511\"><a id=\"m_-7152026281445257199yiv8847588781yui_3_16_0_ym18_1_1458949357220_7691\" class=\"m_-7152026281445257199yiv8847588781edited-link-editor\" href=\"http://goo.gl/forms/PJjwV4MRuO\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?hl=en&amp;q=http://goo.gl/forms/PJjwV4MRuO&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1480884887727000&amp;usg=AFQjCNHqYyGAPg25Pey7jkVCrHaJPrc9Mw\">here</a></span>, and you can vote for what game you want to be played the following week&nbsp;<a id=\"m_-7152026281445257199yiv8847588781yui_3_16_0_ym18_1_1458949357220_9377\" class=\"m_-7152026281445257199yiv8847588781edited-link-editor\" href=\"http://goo.gl/forms/xrhP8sd5jC\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?hl=en&amp;q=http://goo.gl/forms/xrhP8sd5jC&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1480884887727000&amp;usg=AFQjCNHWVsIRTWoehdR0C_SFkqjw_c1vPA\">here</a><span id=\"m_-7152026281445257199yiv8847588781yui_3_16_0_ym18_1_1458949357220_7395\" class=\"m_-7152026281445257199yiv8847588781Apple-converted-s