199yiv8847588781yui_3_16_0_ym18_1_1458949357220_7287\">Other relevant links:</div>\n<div id=\"m_-7152026281445257199yiv8847588781yui_3_16_0_ym18_1_1458949357220_7285\"><span id=\"m_-7152026281445257199yiv8847588781yui_3_16_0_ym18_1_1458949357220_8557\"><a id=\"m_-7152026281445257199yiv8847588781yui_3_16_0_ym18_1_1458949357220_8556\" class=\"m_-7152026281445257199yiv8847588781edited-link-editor\" href=\"https://twitter.com/CinemaQuestria\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?hl=en&amp;q=https://twitter.com/CinemaQuestria&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1480884887727000&amp;usg=AFQjCNFf_wkNy3Cy5eqjRMIH_o8BXMogqg\">Twitter</a></span></div>\n<div id=\"m_-7152026281445257199yiv8847588781yui_3_16_0_ym18_1_1458949357220_7394\" dir=\"ltr\"><span id=\"m_-7152026281445257199yiv8847588781yui_3_16_0_ym18_1_1458949357220_8920\"><a id=\"m_-7152026281445257199yiv8847588781yui_3_16_0_ym18_1_1458949357220_8919\" class=\"m_-7152026281445257199yiv8847588781edited-link-editor\" href=\"http://cinemaquestria.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?hl=en&amp;q=http://cinemaquestria.com/&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1480884887728000&amp;usg=AFQjCNEacOdGSqeJyOWbeRscbns1bTw-cg\">CQ homepage</a></span></div>',27,'2016-12-04 02:00:03','2016-12-03 21:08:43'),
('New Equestria',NULL,'Server','Minecraft',NULL,'<div>We\'ve been working three years for our server called New Equestria. It is a My Little Pony Roleplay themed Minecraft Server, with optional survival or hybrid play with economy between both play styles. Our website can be found here:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://newequestria.com/\" target=\"_blank\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?hl=en&amp;q=http://newequestria.com&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1496874239192000&amp;usg=AFQjCNFF8F7iitJenrvuGyGImhpxj2tTBA\">http://newequestria.com</a></div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>We\'ve made everything from the ground up being completely original in every aspect, from building the landscape in world painter, to placing every individual block. As well as all the content generated such as the art, website and videos, those that are credited we requested their works or got permission from them directly. We pride ourselves of being consistent and making everything from our own hooves.</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>Here you can live your dream of being a Citizen of Equestria, fulfilling your role with whichever job you decide to take up based on your race.</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>Brief overview of all races:</div>\n<div><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLpZxw5bHDHWcV9oylozjVsaoShgYv3xCc\" target=\"_blank\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?hl=en&amp;q=https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list%3DPLpZxw5bHDHWcV9oylozjVsaoShgYv3xCc&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1496874239192000&amp;usg=AFQjCNGIG_pPHH4xr7z4Gap9TvQkizo7sQ\">https://www.youtube.com/<wbr />playlist?list=<wbr />PLpZxw5bHDHWcV9oylozjVsaoShgYv<wbr />3xCc</a></div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>There are miscellaneous jobs exclusive to some races such as Pegasi selling wool or snow to ponies or Unicorns selling unique spells in scrolls for any pony to use a few times before they\'re consumed. Earth ponies hold few harvest-ables that every pony needs every now and again that the other races can\'t collect as well.</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>More information:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.minecraftforum.net/forums/servers/pc-servers/768804-my-little-pony-role-play-server\">http://www.minecraftforum.net/forums/servers/pc-servers/768804-my-little-pony-role-play-server</a></div>',28,'2017-06-06 22:58:47','2017-06-06 22:58:47');
