('Cards Against Equestria','http://cardsagainstequestria.com/',NULL,'<p>If you\'ve played Cards Against Humanity here are a bunch of pony cards to add to your deck!</p>','Always updating',42,'2015-03-11 22:41:15','2015-03-11 22:41:15'),
('Pony Duel: The Card Game','http://imgur.com/a/23zOF#1','http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-2uH6G3reCbw/VrEMFLJHAwI/AAAAAAABidw/LwlYHwuaYE8/s1600/unnamed%2B%25286%2529.png','<p>An original casual competitive card game with cool original vector art. Created by Limey Lassen.&nbsp;</p>\n<div>\n<div>Cards download:&nbsp;<a class=\"hoverZoomLink\" href=\"http://imgur.com/a/23zOF#1\" target=\"_blank\">http://imgur.com/a/23zOF#1</a></div>\n<p>Rules video:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xuRQ4yn5bng\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?<wbr />v=xuRQ4yn5bn</a></p>\n<p>Tabletop Sim:</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=420606141\">http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=420606141</a></p>\n</div>','Active?',43,'2016-02-03 06:07:41','2016-02-02 20:09:46'),
('Ticket to Ride: Equestria','http://vikingpony.com/ttr/index.shtml','http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-ipducXgJ6oE/VrERyxDoBXI/AAAAAAABieU/oGTv6z5ljOw/s1600/7d9ebaff-193e-4fc1-8288-28c366c7e403.png','<div>Ticket to Ride is a popular strategy game by Days of Wonder (<a href=\"http://www.daysofwonder.com/tickettoride/en/usa/\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.daysofwonder.com/<wbr />tickettoride/en/usa/</a>) and seeing as how we play it rather frequently here in Bronies-NYC, we figured it would be great to make a custom version for all the pony fans out there.</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>After quite a bit of playtesting, the final version is ready and is available here:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://vikingpony.com/ttr/index.shtml\" target=\"_blank\">http://vikingpony.com/<wbr />ttr/index.shtml</a>&nbsp;- the site includes rules for the expansion, as well as downloads for the map, tickets and tokens needed in addition to the base game. All contributors are credited on-site.</div>','Active',44,'2016-02-02 20:31:07','2016-02-02 20:31:07'),
('Ponies for D&D 5e','https://docs.google.com/document/d/1O1Tbgtc66NKq7bgAsYCL5XN9xjQI-hMDJheBuzuqfiY/edit',NULL,'<p>Equestria is a land rich in magic and wonder. It is home to many intelligent name-giving races that live together across a varied terrain of rolling plains and marshlands to jagged cliffs and snow-capped mountains. It is also a land of danger and the unknown, for there are many unexplored places and many unexplained mysteries that await the brave and foolhardy to venture towards it.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Prepare to embark on a grand adventure across this magical land. It is a journey fraught with perils, but rich in rewards. However, you cannot go it alone. Along the way you will need to find friendship in the most unlikely of places. For friendship is the strongest magic there is in Equestria, and to those who master friendship go the spoils of success.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','Complete',45,'2017-06-07 07:02:30','2017-06-06 23:47:57'),
('Massive Table Top Index','https://docs.google.com/document/d/1H6mEPdV5EJ84nuI0b2yPr-WSJ7NX-SUCRngiTcE9Ew0/edit?usp=sharing',NULL,'<p>Another Index of a ton of pony tabletop games! Some might overlap with what we have here so far, but check it out if you\'ve exhausted our current list.</p>',NULL,46,'2017-06-07 07:06:04','2017-06-06 23:47:54'),
('Tails of Equestria','http://ninjadivision.com/my-little-pony-tails-of-equestria/tails-of-equestria/','https://3.bp.blogspot.com/--1H6CScfsu0/WTc2ABJQRII/AAAAAAAB2V0/c8cwiman8ige47GoQTaPW93BYcV2ZsbPwCLcB/s1600/MLP-Website-Header-900x325.jpg','<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>My Little Pony: Tails of Equestria</strong>&nbsp;is a storytelling pen and paper game for 2 to 6 players. Players create and role-play as pony heroes who explore and seek adventure in the various lands of Equestria. Guided by a Game Master (GM), players adventure together and use the magic of friendship to overcome obstacles as they learn more about each other and the world around them.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With a full-color, hardback, 152-page rulebook outlining character creation, scenarios, play,&nbsp;<strong>Tails of Equestria</strong>&nbsp;brings My Little Pony to life for all who love the magic-filled world of Equestria. Using the rulebook, players are encouraged to create their own pony that represents them. Armed with core skills and special abilities, each player then ventures into the world with their pony peers, forging deeper friendships as they help one another in the whimsical world they create through every action they take.</p>','Complete, more possibly to come',47,'2017-06-07 03:08:59','2017-06-06 23:47:50'),
('Twilight\'s Secret Shipfic Folder','http://secretshipfic.tumblr.com/','https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-ZFx4QKqHLv8/WTc8abWsYrI/AAAAAAAB2WE/ZyhB0zb90a41yzYJ4QDkwe9ZQODtoQhTwCLcB/s1600/download.jpg','<div>The silly card game about badly written Pony romance.</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div><a href=\"https://www.childrenofkefentse.com/\" target=\"_blank\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?hl=en&amp;q=https://www.childrenofkefentse.com/&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1496878360379000&amp;usg=AFQjCNHqoXBLY4ZqtzC71-YYGvI_Gd-tww\">https://www.<wbr />childrenofkefentse.com/</a> (Fan-driven Resurrection, including card database)</div>\n<div><a href=\"http://secretshipfic.tumblr.com/\" target=\"_blank\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?hl=en&amp;q=http://secretshipfic.tumblr.com/&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1496878360379000&amp;usg=AFQjCNH6FMjBvLcH_pMcp3635wiS1DnerA\">http://secretshipfic.tumblr.<wbr />com/</a> (Original Site)</div>',NULL,48,'2017-06-07 03:36:29','2017-06-06 23:47:47');
